node.text: I’m obsessed with this new Blueberry Protein Waffles recipe I just whipped up with @dishitgirldina and our littles love them too! Want to know the secret? @hphood Cottage Cheese with Blueberry, which gives them that perfect blueberry flavor and tons of protein. This year, @hphood is taking cottage cheese recipes head to head through The Cottage Cheese Delicious Duels. Reminder to cast your vote for your favorite recipe in the bracket at deliciousduels.hood.com. For each vote, @hphood will donate one 16 oz. tub of cottage cheese (up to 5,000 tubs) to @foodbankofcny (Food Bank of Central NY) and @gr8bosfoodbank (The Greater Boston Food Bank). Go vote!! #deliciousduels #hoodcottagecheese #ad

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by 💋Danielle💋 on March 10, 2021 tagging @dishitgirldina, and @hphood. May be an image of 2 people, people standing, food and indoor.

node.text: Cottage cheese is my go-to when I need a quick snack or protein boost to satisfy a craving. I’m working with my sister @dishitgirldina (who, you know, is a master in the kitchen!) and @hphood to show you all the ways cottage cheese can be used for a variety of nutritious and delicious meals. So for those who love cottage cheese like I do, or are interested in trying it (do it!), visit deliciousduels.hood.com to find more recipes and vote for your favorite recipe starting today through March 16! For every vote, Hood will donate one 16 oz. tub of Hood Cottage Cheese (up to 5,000 tubs) to @foodbankofcny (Food Bank of Central NY) and @gr8bosfoodbank (The Greater Boston Food Bank).  #deliciousduels #hoodcottagecheese #ad
